Name: SM RCS Monitoring Check
checklistText:
SM RCS Monitoring Check

Panel 2:
	SM RCS He tb (8) - gray

	SM RCS PRIM PRPLNT tb (4) - gray
	SM RCS SEC PRPLNT tb (4) - gray
	RCS IND sel - SM A, B, C, D

Panel 2:
	Check Quads A, B, C, D
		SM RCS PKG TEMP ind - 115°-175°F

		SM RCS He PRESS ind - record
		SM RCS IND sw - He TK TEMP
		SM RCS He TK TEMP ind - record
		SM RCS IND sw - PRPLNT QTY
		SM RCS PRPLNT QTY ind - record
		SM RCS SEC FUEL PRESS ind - 178-192 psia
			(192-207 psia until jets fired after
			orb insertion)

		When SM RCS SEC FUEL PRESS ind - <150 psia
		SM RCS A (B,C,D) SEC FUEL PRESS - OPEN
